An Italian, 59, was yesterday charged with issuing bad cheques and being in the country illegally. Guisseppe Bocus appeared before Malindi principal Magistrate Silvia Wewa and denied the charges.He allegedly issued the cheques on November 30 last year in Malindi. Bocus issued cheques for Sh720,500 to Grasso on his account in Diamond Trust Bank, Malindi, with knowledge that the account had insufficient funds.